<item>
            <title>[PAY-3791] Merchant Provisioning - no SubMerchantAccount record for ProcessorID 0</title>
                <link>https://wellfit.atlassian.net/browse/PAY-3791</link>
                <project id="10016" key="PAY">Payments</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Brett&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; We have been seeing Provisionings that create a WorldPay CP and Datacap entries in SubMerchantAccount tables.&lt;br/&gt;
The assumption was that testing involved manually creating database records and they were created inaccurately&lt;br/&gt;
However, I saw one in Production this AM (6/5/26) when looking at RedHill&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I do not have any additional info for you yet, I just noticed it&#8230; pretty important to deal with.&lt;br/&gt;
I will let the onboarding team know that this onboarding is suspect so they do not try to use it as it will NOT work.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;Also including SQL and Image&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; *	
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; Payments.SubMerchants
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; SubMerchantName &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;LIKE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;%Rossville%&apos;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; *	
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; Payments.SubMerchantAccounts
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; SubMerchantId = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;67D20000-8D70-7CED-03FE-08DEC249EBEE&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wellfit.atlassian.net/rest/api/3/attachment/content/107611&quot; alt=&quot;image-20260615-143153.png&quot; width=&quot;886&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
